OL,3,CFormer mounted police charged with
OL,4,Cchild rape
OL,6,FTwo former mounted police officers
OL,7,Fhave been charged with the rape of a
OL,8,Fgirl in the 1990s.
OL,10,FThe two men are accused of raping and
OL,11,Fassaulting a girl under the age of 16
OL,12,Fa total of 15 times between 1992 and
OL,13,F1995.
OL,15,FThe offences are alleged to have
OL,16,Fhappened while they were working in
OL,17,Fthe Mounted Section of West Yorkshire
OL,18,FPolice, based in Pontefract.
