OL,3,CFormer mounted police charged with
OL,4,Cchild rape
OL,6,FFormer police sergeant William Baker,
OL,7,F78, has been charged with three counts
OL,8,Fof indecent assault and two counts of
OL,9,Frape against a girl under the age of
OL,10,F16.
OL,12,FFormer police constable Ian Hopkinson,
OL,13,F63, has been charged with five counts
OL,14,Fof indecent assault and five counts of
OL,15,Frape of the same girl.
OL,17,FA woman came forward in 2023 and
OL,18,Freported being the victim of serious
OL,19,Fsexual offences and both men were
OL,20,Farrested on 27 June 2024.
