OL,6,FThey're due to appear at Leeds
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on 7 May.
OL,9,FA third man, 74, was also arrested as
OL,10,Fpart of this investigation. This man,
OL,11,Fwho was also a West Yorkshire Police
OL,12,Fofficer at the time of the alleged
OL,13,Foffences, has since died.
OL,15,FIt was determined there were no
OL,16,Fsuspicious circumstances surrounding
OL,17,Fhis death.
